{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"444797-where-is-your-school","title":"Where Is Your School?","description":"Schools are not just for kids! On his way to school, Pintoo finds some interesting schools! Do you want to see them? Look inside!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sai Keskar"],"illustrators":["Sushant Ahire"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/444797-where-is-your-school"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727493/size3/21776053ccf55e215d97c6b50d6c8bc5.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727493/size6/21776053ccf55e215d97c6b50d6c8bc5.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/468875/size6/fcd43f8c8c65b4fbfb05dbd1214499e6.jpg","text":"I go to school every\nday.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/468877/size6/53e9e16dc477d014cc97f1d17cd67be6.jpg","text":"Chiki and I see\nmany schools on our way.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460766/size6/6c551cf23a35dab4d00e61ea247fd8c2.jpg","text":"The parrots fly to\na school on a guava tree.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460768/size6/39bf0e7aa77ad859d5a12a6dc89ac4bc.jpg","text":"The squirrels\nrun to\na school\non a mango tree.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460769/size6/9dd574a56010b7ddffe320efb973423d.jpg","text":"The pigeons sit in a\nschool on electric wires","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460773/size6/b55bd417afb81daac7b478ca72af764e.jpg","text":"The ducks float in a\nschool on the lake.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460775/size6/d8fafb5605eaf2c44e1109f0fe4c5df2.jpg","text":"Baby cows walk to a\nschool in a field.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460776/size6/16d32f533695a65c88bfb7117bb52a71.jpg","text":"Can you see the tamarind tree?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460777/size6/730f1901066c157846d73b9e1c9973e9.jpg","text":"My school is under\nthat tree.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/461849/size6/a0a0cf7fc21f261594d4432543dffbef.jpg","text":"And the crows are\nabove me.\nIn a school on the tamarind tree!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460827/size6/2ceb308b60c72399393f1a1cf47595f8.jpg","text":"Chiki\ngoes to school on Sundays.\nIn my home!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/467741/size6/c4be7624dda5a7b7e66ec108fe825762.jpg","text":"No books and no\nschoolbag for her.\nIn the home school, I am her teacher!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/460783/size6/9b255a127b13eac64612b0a621454592.jpg","text":"14/14","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":13,"words":112}}